            <span class="font-mono text-xs text-mute font-normal">03.</span>
            <span>What is the point of fruit merge game?</span>
          </span>
          <span class="text-mute group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256">
              <path d="M216.49,104.49l-80,80a12,12,0,0,1-17,0l-80-80a12,12,0,0,1,17-17L128,159l71.51-71.52a12,12,0,0,1,17,17Z"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-5 pb-5 text-body text-xs md:text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-hairline/50 pt-4">
          <p>
            The point of the fruit merge game is to stack and combine matching fruits to earn points and clear space. Because fruits grow larger with each merge, space management is crucial. If the pile overflows the red boundary line, the game is over.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

