            To play the fruit merge game:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-decimal pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Move your mouse or swipe on your screen to position the active fruit preview.</li>
            <li>Click or tap to drop the fruit into the container.</li>
            <li>When two of the same fruits collide, they automatically combine and grow into the next-level fruit (e.g. Cherry to Strawberry, Strawberry to Grape).</li>
            <li>Avoid letting the fruit pile overflow the top red line.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
      <details class="group border border-hairline bg-canvas hover:border-hairline-strong transition-all duration-200 rounded-lg">
