            To win the fruit merge game, you must successfully combine fruits all the way up to create a giant Watermelon. Since the game is endless and can continue even after creating a watermelon, "winning" is also defined by achieving the highest score possible. Keep large fruits at the bottom and small fruits on top to maximize your space.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 8 -->
