            Winning the fruit merge match game requires patience and strategy. Focus on creating combos where smaller fruits cascade into larger ones. Always try to keep your largest fruits on one side (or at the bottom) so they don't block smaller fruits from merging.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- FAQ Item 9 -->
