            Winning the fruit merge game is all about physics and order. Here are the top tips:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Group fruits of similar sizes near each other.</li>
            <li>Avoid trapping tiny cherries under large melons.</li>
            <li>Make use of power-ups like <strong>Shake</strong> to settle fruits, <strong>Clear Cherries</strong> to clear clutter, and <strong>Magic Upgrade</strong> to resolve blockages.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </details>

