        <div class="px-5 pb-5 text-body text-xs md:text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-hairline/50 pt-4">
          <p>
            To beat the fruit merge game and create the giant watermelon:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Place your fruits carefully, predicting their bounce.</li>
            <li>Plan merges in advance; when a fruit merges, it grows in size and pushes other fruits aside.</li>
            <li>Keep the middle or sides clear of tiny fruits that can block larger merges.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </details>

