            </svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-5 pb-5 text-body text-xs md:text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-hairline/50 pt-4">
          <p>
            While the core gameplay of the <strong>fruit merge match game</strong> is completely family-friendly and safe for all ages, some mobile clones on app stores carry a 17+ rating. This rating is usually due to aggressive third-party ads, in-app purchases, simulated gambling, or open community features in those specific app store downloads. The web version here at Fruit Gamer is ad-free, secure, and suitable for all age groups.
          </p>
        </div>
      </details>

